# Tsumugi Project Rules

Read `AGENTS.md` and `docs/agent-instructions.md` before making changes.

## Key Rules

- Rust stable only (no nightly)
- Small PRs (300 lines max)
- Conventional Commits (`feat:`, `fix:`, `chore:`)
- Tests required for features
- Crate isolation: traits for communication, one-way dependencies
- Biome for TS/JS (not ESLint/Prettier)
- GitHub Actions: SHA-pinned only
- Verify: `make lint` and `make test` before completing
